		<Enumeration Name="AcquisitionMode" NameSpace="Standard">
			<ToolTip>Sets the acquisition mode of the device.</ToolTip>
			<Description>Sets the acquisition mode of the device. It defines mainly the number of frames
				to capture during an acquisition and the way the acquisition stops.</Description>
